{"tid":628837,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警車違泊阻街被抄牌","createTime":"2018-04-14T08:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T08:54:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b296e557d634e50739149830fd888edefee08d4b","tid":628837,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T08:21:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180414/20361078?_ga=2.36293408.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F20361078%3F_ga%3D2.36293408.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=as0WiOeuhvz8opnM8qFyT3adZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=94c454d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F20361078%3F_ga%3D2.36293408.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=92177770\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180414/20361078?_ga=2.36293408.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n警車違泊阻街被抄牌<br />\n<br />\n15K<br />\n要聞<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】大埔昨發生警車被抄牌事件，有市民昨中午發現多輛車輛於寶湖里違泊阻街，於是報警。交通督導員前往處理，並於上址發出8張俗稱「牛肉乾」的交通違例定額罰款通知書，其間聯絡不到警車所屬單位，於是向警車抄牌。警方昨晚承認涉事警車當時前往處理一宗糾紛及有人意外受傷事件，事後已駕走警車。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180414/large/a0802a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180414%2Flarge%2Fa0802a.gif&h=88ad0d3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警車被抄牌的照片在網上流傳。<br />\n互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n按法例獲豁免交通限制<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，昨中午12時許，警方接報到大埔寶湖里處理案件時，將警車停泊於寶湖里1號對開路邊，警方強調當時該處並無車輛阻塞。其後另有8輛車輛到上址停泊並出現交通擠塞，有市民報警，當時有交通督導員奉召前往處理，其間交通督導員向在場8輛違泊車輛發出定額罰款通知書。<br />\n<br />\n據知，當時交通督導員見有警車停泊在上址，曾聯絡警方但不成功，於是按法例規定向警車發出告票。其間有市民拍下警車被抄牌的照片上載社交群組，成為熱話。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，涉事警車的警員其後完成處理案件後，發現被抄牌亦將警車駛離。警方發言人證實事件，並指經常提醒前線人員在執行職務期間需留意路面交通情況，盡量避免影響交通及其他道路使用者。<br />\n<br />\n根據現行法例，警隊車輛獲豁免有關泊車及交通標誌或道路標誌的限制；換言之，該告票會獲取消。<br />\n<br />\n■記者關英傑"},{"pid":"ccc38369e728937fffe8f8f5c8b1e42feb2225e0","tid":628837,"uid":26937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T08:24:00.000Z","msg":"成篇新聞有乜意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0735356410b0a868a843f2940643bbf812f48545","tid":628837,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccc38369e728937fffe8f8f5c8b1e42feb2225e0","tid":628837,"uid":26937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T08:24:00.000Z","msg":"成篇新聞有乜意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T08:33:05.000Z","msg":"俾班反警打兩秒j"},{"pid":"48b53c35de6c45c91f60633cdffd74c214e3f564","tid":628837,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T08:54:12.000Z","msg":"樓主硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=27225035&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}